For Jenkins Slave 

Step-1: Need to create Master Jenkins
Step-2: In Master create public and private key
Step-3: Create Slave machine 
Step-4: In slave machine create a (Directory)
Step-4: Go to Manage Jenkins and Click (Nodes) 
--> Need to give the (Ip address), (Crendentails), (PrivateKey)
Step-5: Add crendentails for the (Slave) machine    # What crendentails need to create for the slave 
--> User name like (ec2-user,Ubuntu)
--> Private Key where you created the AWS private key
